articles.author: Julia Horowitz
articles.title: Europe's economy ticks up in the first quarter - CNN
articles.description: Europe's economy avoided a recession over the winter, picking up pace slightly in the first quarter of 2023 despite Russia's war in Ukraine and sizable interest rate hikes aimed at fighting inflation.
